'.source.gfm':
  '[^ref](text)':
    'prefix': 'lia.footnote inline'
    'body': '[^${1:ref}](${2:explanation})'
    'description': """
    Inline Footnotes are composed of a reference in brackets with a starting caret. The following text has to be put into parentheses, only one line is allowed.

       Example with [^1](inline _footnote_) and some more text.
    """
    'descriptionMoreURL': 'https://liascript.github.io/course/?https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liaScript/docs/master/README.md'
    'leftLabelHTML': '<span style="color:#ff0">ðŸ¦‰</span>'

  '[^ref]':
    'prefix': 'lia.footnote.reference'
    'body': '[^${1:ref}]'
    'description': """
    Multiline footnotes have to be split into a reference and into a comments. Footnote references are defined by brackets with a starting caret and can appear everywhere within the text. Footnote texts have to be put into the end of each section.

    Example:

    Here is a footnote reference, [^1] and another.[^longnote]

    ...

    [^1]: Here is the footnote text.

    [^longnote]: Here's one with multiple blocks.

                   Subsequent paragraphs are indented to show that they
                   belong to the previous footnote.
    """
    'descriptionMoreURL': 'https://liascript.github.io/course/?https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liaScript/docs/master/README.md'
    'leftLabelHTML': '<span style="color:#ff0">ðŸ¦‰</span>'

  '[^ref]: some comments ...':
    'prefix': 'lia.footnote.text'
    'body': '[^${1:ref}]: ${2:some comments}'
    'description': """
    Multiline footnotes have to be split into a reference and into a comments. Footnote texts start with a reference "tag", which is followed by a colon. They have to be put into the end of each section otherwise they are not interpreted as footnote texts and multiblock footnotes have to follow the previous identation.

    Example:
    ...

    [^1]: Here is the footnote text.

    [^longnote]: Here's one with multiple blocks.

                   Subsequent paragraphs are indented to show that they
                   belong to the previous footnote.
    """
    'descriptionMoreURL': 'https://liascript.github.io/course/?https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liaScript/docs/master/README.md'
    'leftLabelHTML': '<span style="color:#ff0">ðŸ¦‰</span>'
